definition: method of calculating a person's age in years from birth/see also 虛歲|虚岁[xu1 sui4]/see also 實歲|实岁[shi2 sui4]
classifier for years (of age)/year/year (of crop harvests)

sentences.english: But how could we disguise the fact that I was not [even] fifteen years old?
sentences.chinese: 可我們怎麼才能掩飾我還不到15足歲的事實呢？
